    "About MatchMondo" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "MatchMondoについて"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Built by a group of passionate football fans in California who wanted a better way to follow the 2026 World Cup. We built this app for ourselves — and we're grateful anyone else has found it useful." : {
      "comment" : "About section body",
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "2026年ワールドカップをもっと楽しみたいカリフォルニアのサッカーファンが作りました。自分たちのために作ったアプリですが、皆さんにもお役に立てれば幸いです。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tournament Rules" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "大会ルール"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Support Genesis Oakland" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Genesis Oaklandを応援"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "MatchMondo is free and always will be — no ads, no subscriptions. If you'd like to give back, consider donating to Genesis Oakland — a youth soccer club building community and creating opportunity for kids in Oakland through the beautiful game." : {
      "comment" : "Support section body",
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "MatchMondoは無料で、広告もサブスクもありません。もしお気に召しましたら、Genesis Oakland（オークランドの少年サッカークラブ）への寄付をご検討ください。サッカーを通じてコミュニティと子どもたちの未来を育てています。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Donate to Genesis Oakland" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Genesis Oaklandに寄付する"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Or we can donate for you — just Venmo @busselle and we'll pass along the donation to Genesis Oakland." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "代わりに寄付することもできます。Venmo @busselle にお送りいただければ、Genesis Oaklandにお届けします。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Donate via Venmo (@busselle, 2515)" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Venmoで寄付する（@busselle, 2515）"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Feature Requests" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "機能リクエスト"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Have an idea to make MatchMondo better? We'd love to hear it." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "MatchMondoをもっと良くするアイデアはありますか？ぜひお聞かせください。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Email us a feature request" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "機能リクエストをメールで送る"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "MatchMondo v%@" : {
      "comment" : "App version display",
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "MatchMondo v%@"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Made with ❤️ in California" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "カリフォルニアで❤️を込めて"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A fan's guide to the laws and tournament rules for the 2026 World Cup." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "2026年ワールドカップのルールガイド"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Match Format" : {
      "comment" : "Rules section title",
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "試合形式"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Two 45-minute halves plus stoppage time. Group-stage matches can end in a draw. From the Round of 32 on, a tie after 90 minutes goes to two 15-minute periods of extra time, and if still level, a penalty shootout decides it." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "前後半各45分＋アディショナルタイム。グループステージは引き分けあり。ベスト32以降、90分で同点の場合は前後半各15分の延長戦、それでも決着がつかなければPK戦。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Yellow Card (Caution)" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "イエローカード（警告）"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A warning for unsporting behavior, dissent, persistent fouling, time-wasting, not respecting required distance at free kicks/corners, or entering/leaving the field without permission." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "非スポーツマン行為、異議、繰り返しの反則、時間稼ぎ、フリーキック/コーナーキックでの距離不遵守、無断でのフィールドへの出入りに対する警告。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Red Card (Sending-off)" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "レッドカード（退場）"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Shown for serious foul play, violent conduct, spitting, denying an obvious goal-scoring opportunity, offensive language, or two yellow cards in the same match. The player leaves and cannot be replaced — the team plays short." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "著しく不正なプレー、暴力行為、唾吐き、決定的な得点機会の阻止、侮辱的な言葉、または同一試合で2枚のイエローカード。退場した選手の補充はできず、チームは少人数でプレー。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Suspensions & Amnesty" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "出場停止と累積リセット"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Two yellows in different matches = one-match suspension. Single yellows are wiped after the group stage, and wiped again after the quarter-finals, so a player can't miss the final from an early caution." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "異なる試合での累積イエロー2枚で1試合出場停止。グループステージ終了後と準々決勝後にリセットされるため、初期の警告で決勝を欠場することはありません。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Group Tiebreakers" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "グループ順位の決定方法"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If teams are level on points: 1) Goal difference, 2) Goals scored, 3) Head-to-head points, 4) Head-to-head GD, 5) Head-to-head goals scored, 6) Fair-play score, 7) Drawing of lots." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "勝点が同じ場合：1) 得失点差、2) 総得点、3) 直接対決の勝点、4) 直接対決の得失点差、5) 直接対決の得点、6) フェアプレーポイント、7) 抽選。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Who Advances" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "進出条件"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "48 teams in 12 groups. The top two from each group (24 teams) advance, plus the 8 best third-placed teams — 32 teams into the Round of 32." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "12グループ48チーム。各グループ上位2チーム（計24チーム）と3位の中で成績上位の8チーム、合計32チームがベスト32に進出。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Unofficial summary for fans. See FIFA for official regulations." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ファン向けの非公式まとめです。公式規定はFIFAをご確認ください。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Done" : {
      "comment" : "YouTube sheet dismiss button",
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "完了"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "version" : "1.0"
}
